These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
Food: pineapple, potato, spinach, mango
1. Food:pineapple is on the far left##1
2. Food:potato is on the left or right of Food:pineapple##3
3. Food:potato is on the left or right of Food:spinach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | pineapple | potato | spinach | mango |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, milk
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left of Beverage:juice##1
3. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | milk | juice |

